      <title>据彭博社报道，汇丰银行正在就将南非子公司出售给 FirstRand 进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-talks-sell-south-africa-unit-firstrand-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-13/</link>
